Coverage increased (+0.005%) to 97.225% when pulling **278a358f5114d350ce149354baf2490d1cc5e41a on alefteris:decode-dicts** into **2e4edb55e4905c4f1d8ca30511ca5f613ff7990a on aio-libs:master**.
I don't remember any commands returning dics. What are they?

Redis `HGETALL` command returns array reply,
aioredis `Redis.hgetall` method converts such array reply into dict, decoding is supported as well.
I'm so sorry. Somehow I didn't set the decode for Redis.hgetall and I thought there was an issue with the returned dict. Closing.
